data.text: If you elect to offer the Certificate Services (defined further below) to others, you must agree to and abide by the terms and conditions in this Certificate Services Reseller Agreement (hereinafter, “Cert Reseller Agreement”). This Cert Reseller Agreement is between you, your organization (if you are entering into this Cert Reseller Agreement on behalf of an organization), collectively referred to herein as “you” or “your” (and appropriate formatives), the service provider offering these services to you, if any, (the “Primary Service Provider”) and the backend service provider Secure Business Services, Inc., and Secure Business Services, Inc.’s parent company and upstream service provider(s) (together, the “Backend Service Provider”). You are identified by the contract information you provide to the Primary and/or Backend Service Provider, as the case may be, and not necessarily by the contact information of the party who pays for the Certificate Services.
